# Public feed surface — transparent proxy to khashif-agent backend.
# Buyer sees khashif.run/feed/*; data still served from Render. Brand
# stays on the studio domain. Added 27 May 2026 alongside the public
# markdown feeds in app.py. Substrate bridge for Memory Block Kit v1
# (B-model integration — buyer's frontier reads khashif.run/feed/* as
# ambient context).
#
# Status 200 = rewrite (transparent proxy). The URL bar stays on
# khashif.run; the response body is served from khashif-agent.

/feed/*    https://khashif-agent.onrender.com/feed/:splat    200
/feed      https://khashif-agent.onrender.com/feed           200
/feed.xml  https://khashif-agent.onrender.com/feed.xml       200
/rss       https://khashif-agent.onrender.com/rss            200
